{"tid":1278131,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"鄭若驊老公公司上市","createTime":"2019-07-02T11:10:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-02T11:14:43.000Z","uid":66811,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"2765a9fcf28c006263e3f53261c03314e87585f9","tid":1278131,"uid":66811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T11:10:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.finsight-ed.com/2019/07/02/%E9%84%AD%E8%8B%A5%E9%A9%8A%E8%80%81%E5%85%AC%E4%B8%8A%E5%B8%82%E9%9A%A8%E6%99%82%E6%BB%91%E9%90%B5%E7%9B%A7%EF%BC%9F/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.finsight-ed.com%2F2019%2F07%2F02%2F%25E9%2584%25AD%25E8%258B%25A5%25E9%25A9%258A%25E8%2580%2581%25E5%2585%25AC%25E4%25B8%258A%25E5%25B8%2582%25E9%259A%25A8%25E6%2599%2582%25E6%25BB%2591%25E9%2590%25B5%25E7%259B%25A7%25EF%25BC%259F%2F&d=vndMBExpkEaUQx9ttGHWPtqUVvxpOm%2FTDjh67WAJGsM%3D&h=1108015f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.finsight-ed.com/2019/07/02/%E9%84%AD%E8%8B%A5%E9%A9%8A%E8%80%81%E5%85%AC%E4%B8%8A%E5%B8%82%E9%9A%A8%E6%99%82%E6%BB%91%E9%90%B5%E7%9B%A7%EF%BC%9F/</a><br />\n<br />\n既然安樂工程有這個集資需要，那麼為什麼集團要在上市前兩年派發巨額股息呢？ 上市公司上市前一般會向股東派發股息，避免保留太多現金，上市後等同送錢予投資者。但安樂工程連續兩年共派發接近13億元予股東，然後又來上市集資，究竟公司本身是否存在集資需要呢？<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n事實上，過去一年，港交所就曾經因為「沒有需要上市的商業理據，並非真有集資需要」為理由，拒絕15名申請人的上市申請。"},{"pid":"82285d39f8d0dc740958f862985e9c2dc7e138d4","tid":1278131,"uid":259700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-02T11:14:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}